snippet.title: DDLC *Gone Wrong!* | Doki Doki MalignancY
snippet.description:
Doki Doki Malignancy is a mod what was made in 48 hours (yes im not kidding) and it probably has the best art work i have ever seen in  a DDLC mod! Doki Doki Malignancy will be remember for a long time to come as one of the best DDLC Mods ever created!
